pr_title: Added basic auth for admin controller
pr_body: I have copy-pasted some code and do not fully understand how this works, but it does work. `AdminController` requires authentication to be able to perform any requests and `ContigController` works without authentication. Tests in `AdminControllerIntegrationTest` are broken because `MockMVC` isn't able to authenticate with the controller. I'm looking into how to do that now. Related issue #15

I have also added a static assembly report at src/test/resources/GCF_000003055.4_Bos_taurus_UMD_3.1_assembly_report.txt to run tests on.
